Of course=C2=A0a little Twitter fun is worth $37 million to the world=E2=80=
=99s richest and most Twitter-obsessed human.=09Isn=E2=80=99t this really=
=C2=A0good=C2=A0disclosure? Another quite sensible and valid complaint that=
