rading at a $7=C2=A0billion valuation=C2=A0now, but it could go below $875 =
million=C2=A0later. That=E2=80=99s entirely possible, given that it is an i=
maginary company.=C2=A0It has disclosed no financial information, no busine=
ss plans, no nothing; the market=E2=80=99s belief that it is worth $7=C2=A0=
billion is based on political loyalty and memes and some vague bluster from=
