ments, operations, business plans, any of that stuff that companies have to=
 disclose before going public, and that disclosure is bad =E2=80=94=C2=A0th=
en the stock might drop, but you don=E2=80=99t get to change your mind. Let=
's also assume that you have to agree to lock up your shares for a while af=
