er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">the announcement of the deal</a>: =E2=80=9CTh=
e transaction values Trump Media &amp; Technology Group at an initial enter=
prise value of $875 Million.=E2=80=9D The <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloo=
mbergbusiness.com/click/25665904.269658/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZ=
lcy9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzAwMDE4NDk2MzUvMDAwMTE5MzEyNTIxMzA4MTQ2L2QyMzAyMjFkZXgyMS=
